
XML Data to Daily Email Alert
Scripting & Automation
Posted 5 days ago
Worldwide
I require a simple system to be created that checks an XML file (which is updated daily on a government website) for any changes, then emails said changes to us each day.

The data comes from here: https://ratings.food.gov.uk/open-data/ with the specific XML file being https://ratings.food.gov.uk/OpenDataFiles/FHRS867en-GB.xml.

Guidance can be found here: https://www.food.gov.uk/sites/default/files/media/document/fhrs-api1-guidance.pdf

